  "prompt": "What are some good and romantic Malayalam songs?",
  "response": "Malayalam cinema has a rich tradition of beautiful romantic songs that convey deep emotions and love. Here are some popular and romantic Malayalam songs that you might enjoy:\n\n1. **\"Premioodle\"** - *Lailaa O Lailaa*\n2. **\"Maanathe Chayank riche\"** - *Parinayam*\n3. **\"Putham Pudhu Kaalai\"** - *Ayalum Njanum Thammil*\n4. **\"Venmegham Vennilave\"** - *Mithunam*\n5. **\"Neeyum Njanum\"** - *Kadhaparayumpol*\n6. **\"Sundariye\"** - *Naranathu Thampuran*\n7. **\"Thamarakannan\"** - *Oru Vadakkan Veeragatha*\n8. **\"Minu Minakkum\"** - *Satyam*\n9. **\"Kaithaparam\"** - *Aadhyaayam*\n10. **\"Vennilave Vennilave\"** - *Madhuranaranga*\n\nThese songs showcase various styles and themes of romance, capturing the essence of love in lyrical beauty. Enjoy listening!",
